📌 VIERA (Vocational English Rating)
   → Tes bahasa Inggris khusus untuk siswa SMK di Indonesia
   → Menguji Reading, Listening, dan Grammar dasar
   → Level: Beginner sampai Advanced
   → Relevan dengan dunia kerja di jurusan masing-masing (RPL = IT/Tech context)

📌 TOEIC (Test of English for International Communication)
   → Tes internasional untuk dunia kerja
   → Skor: 10–990 (target kamu: setinggi mungkin)
   → Bagian: Listening (495 poin) + Reading (495 poin)
   → Format:
      Part 1: Photographs — 6 soal (Listening)
      Part 2: Question-Response — 25 soal (Listening)
      Part 3: Short Conversations — 39 soal (Listening)
      Part 4: Short Talks — 30 soal (Listening)
      Part 5: Incomplete Sentences — 30 soal (Reading/Grammar)
      Part 6: Text Completion — 16 soal (Reading/Grammar)
      Part 7: Reading Comprehension — 54 soal (Reading)

Materi grammar yang paling sering diuji di TOEIC Part 5 & 6:
   1. Word Forms (bentuk kata)
   2. Subject-Verb Agreement
   3. Passive Voice
   4. Prepositions
   5. Modal Verbs
   6. Tenses (terutama Simple Present, Past, dan Perfect)
   7. Conjunctions
   8. Gerund & Infinitive

