Soal 1: Tentukan kelas kata dari kata yang dicetak KAPITAL
a) The MANAGER sent a detailed report.
b) She works EFFICIENTLY under pressure.
c) Please submit YOUR application by Monday.
d) The new software is RELIABLE.
e) They updated the system QUICKLY.

Soal 2: Pilih kata yang tepat (TOEIC Style)
1. Please send the proposal to _____ as soon as possible.
   (A) I    (B) me    (C) my    (D) mine

2. The report was written _____.
   (A) careful    (B) care    (C) carefully    (D) caring

3. The _____ of the new system surprised everyone.
   (A) efficient    (B) efficiently    (C) efficiency    (D) efficiencies

JAWABAN:
Soal 1:
a) MANAGER = Noun
b) EFFICIENTLY = Adverb (menerangkan cara kerja)
c) YOUR = Possessive Adjective (Pronoun)
d) RELIABLE = Adjective (menerangkan "software")
e) QUICKLY = Adverb (menerangkan "updated")

Soal 2:
1. (B) me — setelah "to" gunakan object pronoun
2. (C) carefully — menerangkan verb "was written", butuh adverb
3. (C) efficiency — setelah "The", butuh noun

