MATERI 4: PRONOUNS (Kata Ganti — Deep Study)
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

Prasyarat: Materi 1
Kaitan TOEIC: SANGAT SERING — salah pilih pronoun adalah jebakan klasik

TABEL LENGKAP PRONOUN:

Subjek  | Subject | Object | Poss.Adj | Poss.Pron | Reflexive
I       | I       | me     | my       | mine      | myself
You     | you     | you    | your     | yours     | yourself
He      | he      | him    | his      | his       | himself
She     | she     | her    | her      | hers      | herself
It      | it      | it     | its      | its       | itself
We      | we      | us     | our      | ours      | ourselves
They    | they    | them   | their    | theirs    | themselves

CARA PAKAI:

Subject Pronoun (sebelum verb):
   I sent the email. / She approved the budget. / They finished early.

Object Pronoun (setelah verb atau preposition):
   Please contact me. / The boss praised her. / We rely on them.

Possessive Adjective (sebelum noun):
   My report is ready. / His password expired. / Their team won.

Possessive Pronoun (berdiri sendiri, tanpa noun):
   This laptop is mine. / That office is hers. / The idea was theirs.

Reflexive Pronoun:
   He taught himself coding. (sendiri)
   The system updated itself. (otomatis)
   She introduced herself to the client. (memperkenalkan diri)

TOEIC TRAP #1 — Its vs It's:
   its = possessive (kepemilikan): The company updated its website.
   it's = it is: It's time to restart the server.

TOEIC TRAP #2 — Their vs They're vs There:
   their = possessive: Their project is done.
   they're = they are: They're working overtime.
   there = tempat atau there is/are: There is a problem.

TOEIC TRAP #3 — Pilihan Subject/Object:
   ❌ Her and me went to the meeting.
   ✅ She and I went to the meeting. (keduanya sebagai subjek)

   ❌ The boss emailed he and I.
   ✅ The boss emailed him and me. (keduanya sebagai objek)

Trik cek: Hapus salah satu pronoun, lihat mana yang terasa benar.
   "The boss emailed ... I" → terasa salah
   "The boss emailed ... me" → benar → gunakan "me"

