━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

Prasyarat: Materi 3
Kaitan TOEIC: Part 1 Listening (deskripsi gambar)

FUNGSI: Digunakan untuk menyatakan keberadaan sesuatu

Rumus:
   There IS + singular noun (benda tunggal)
   There ARE + plural noun (benda jamak)

Contoh:
   There is a new employee in the IT department.
   There are three meetings scheduled for today.
   There is an error in the code.
   There are several files missing from the server.

Bentuk Negatif:
   There is no internet connection right now.
   There are no available conference rooms.
   There isn't enough storage space.
   There aren't any updates available.

Bentuk Pertanyaan:
   Is there a problem with the system?
   Are there any files I need to review?
   Is there a backup of the database?

Bentuk Past:
   There was a power outage yesterday.
   There were many bugs in the previous version.

TOEIC TRAP — Singular vs Plural:
   ❌ There are a new notification.
   ✅ There is a new notification.

   ❌ There is many users online.
   ✅ There are many users online.

