CONJUNCTION CHEAT SHEET — TOEIC:
Jika kamu melihat... pilih...
   Kontras (situasi berlawanan) → although/even though/despite/however
   Sebab (kenapa?) → because/since/due to/because of
   Tujuan (untuk apa?) → so that/in order to/to
   Syarat (kalau) → if/unless/provided that
   Waktu → when/while/before/after/until

