MATERI 23: CONDITIONALS (Kalimat Pengandaian)
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

Prasyarat: Semua tense, modal verbs

─────────────────────────────────────────────
TYPE 0: FAKTA/KEBENARAN UMUM
─────────────────────────────────────────────
Rumus: If + Simple Present, Simple Present
   If you restart the computer, it works better.
   If the server overheats, it shuts down automatically.
   (ini selalu benar, seperti hukum alam/fakta)

─────────────────────────────────────────────
TYPE 1: KONDISI NYATA/MUNGKIN TERJADI
─────────────────────────────────────────────
Rumus: If + Simple Present, will + V1
   If we upgrade the server, the performance will improve.
   If she attends the training, she will get certified.
   If the budget is approved, we will hire more developers.

─────────────────────────────────────────────
TYPE 2: KONDISI TIDAK NYATA (SEKARANG/MASA DEPAN)
─────────────────────────────────────────────
Rumus: If + Simple Past, would + V1
(situasi yang tidak nyata, atau sangat kecil kemungkinannya)
   If I were the manager, I would increase the budget. (saya bukan manager)
   If we had more time, we would test it more thoroughly. (kenyataannya tidak punya waktu)
   If the system were faster, we could serve more clients.

   PENTING: Gunakan "were" untuk semua subjek (bukan "was") dalam formal writing
   ❌ If I was rich, I would buy a new server.
   ✅ If I were rich, I would buy a new server.

─────────────────────────────────────────────
TYPE 3: KONDISI TIDAK NYATA DI MASA LALU
─────────────────────────────────────────────
Rumus: If + Past Perfect (had + V3), would have + V3
(menyesal tentang sesuatu yang sudah terjadi atau tidak terjadi)
   If we had backed up the data, we wouldn't have lost everything.
   If she had attended the training, she would have been promoted.
   If they had tested the system properly, the launch would have been successful.

