MATERI 27: DISCOURSE MARKERS
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

Prasyarat: Conjunctions
Kaitan TOEIC: Part 6 (text completion) sangat sering!

Discourse markers adalah kata/frasa yang menunjukkan HUBUNGAN antara ide dalam teks.
Di TOEIC Part 6, kamu sering diminta memilih discourse marker yang tepat.

PENAMBAHAN (untuk menambah informasi):
   furthermore, moreover, in addition, additionally, besides, also, what is more
   
   The new software is more efficient. Furthermore, it is also more affordable.
   In addition to the technical skills, she has excellent communication abilities.

KONTRAS (untuk menunjukkan pertentangan):
   however, on the other hand, nevertheless, nonetheless, in contrast, yet, still
   
   The project was expensive. However, the results were worth it.
   On the other hand, some employees prefer the old system.

SEBAB/HASIL (untuk menunjukkan hubungan sebab-akibat):
   therefore, as a result, consequently, thus, hence, for this reason
   
   The server was down for 2 hours. As a result, we lost significant revenue.
   The deadline was moved forward; therefore, we need to work overtime.

CONTOH:
   for example, for instance, such as, namely, including
   
   Please avoid unnecessary software, such as games and media players.
   Many professionals use productivity tools. For example, Slack and Trello are popular.

URUTAN:
   firstly/first, secondly, thirdly, then, next, after that, finally, lastly
   
   Firstly, check the network connection. Then, restart the router. Finally, test the speed.

KESIMPULAN:
   in conclusion, to sum up, overall, in summary, in brief, to conclude
   
   In conclusion, the new system has improved productivity by 30%.

PENGAKUAN/KONSESI:
   admittedly, granted that, even so, all the same, that said
   
   Admittedly, the project was delayed. That said, the final product exceeded expectations.

