MATERI 29: WORD FORMS (Bentuk Kata)
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

Kaitan TOEIC: Part 5 PALING SERING — hampir setiap tes ada 3-5 soal!

INI ADALAH MATERI NOMOR SATU YANG PALING SERING KELUAR DI TOEIC.
Strategi: Lihat posisi kata dalam kalimat → tentukan kelas kata yang dibutuhkan → pilih bentuk yang tepat.

─────────────────────────────────────────────
CARA MENJAWAB SOAL WORD FORM:
─────────────────────────────────────────────
Langkah 1: Baca kalimatnya, temukan celah (blank)
Langkah 2: Lihat apa yang ADA DI SEKITAR blank:
   - Setelah "the/a/an" → butuh NOUN atau ADJECTIVE
   - Setelah "is/was/are/were" → butuh ADJECTIVE atau NOUN (atau V3 untuk passive)
   - Sebelum noun → butuh ADJECTIVE
   - Setelah noun → BISA butuh verb (verb dalam kalimat itu)
   - Menerangkan verb → butuh ADVERB
Langkah 3: Pilih bentuk kata yang sesuai

─────────────────────────────────────────────
AKHIRAN NOUN (Kata Benda):
─────────────────────────────────────────────
-tion / -sion: information, communication, presentation, submission, decision, permission
-ity: productivity, reliability, flexibility, ability, quality, security, creativity
-ness: effectiveness, awareness, willingness, happiness, weakness
-ment: management, development, improvement, achievement, employment
-ance / -ence: performance, assistance, preference, conference, experience, difference
-er / -or: manager, developer, designer, director, supervisor, operator, instructor
-ist: specialist, analyst, journalist, programmer (tergantung kata)
-ship: leadership, partnership, membership, relationship
-ry / -ery: discovery, delivery, industry, machinery

─────────────────────────────────────────────
AKHIRAN ADJECTIVE (Kata Sifat):
─────────────────────────────────────────────
-ful: successful, helpful, useful, careful, powerful, meaningful, skillful
-less: careless, useless, wireless, endless, thoughtless, powerless
-ous / -ious: famous, dangerous, serious, ambitious, various, previous
-al / -ical: professional, technical, digital, logical, practical, critical
-able / -ible: reliable, available, accessible, responsible, flexible, compatible
-ive / -ative: creative, productive, effective, innovative, administrative, communicative
-ent / -ant: efficient, important, significant, relevant, different, independent
-ed: experienced, qualified, dedicated, limited, advanced (sering berasal dari verb)
-ing: interesting, challenging, demanding, rewarding (sering berasal dari verb)

─────────────────────────────────────────────
AKHIRAN VERB (Kata Kerja):
─────────────────────────────────────────────
-ize / -ise: organize, prioritize, maximize, minimize, customize, analyze
-ify: qualify, clarify, justify, simplify, notify, verify, identify
-en: strengthen, broaden, widen, deepen, tighten
-ate: communicate, evaluate, estimate, coordinate, facilitate, participate

─────────────────────────────────────────────
AKHIRAN ADVERB (Kata Keterangan):
─────────────────────────────────────────────
-ly: efficiently, professionally, carefully, successfully, significantly, recently
   (hampir selalu: adjective + -ly = adverb)
   PENGECUALIAN: good → well (bukan goodly)

